<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Ledor</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-10-10 22:06:13</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I do agree with the other posts about the GREAT exp you get at these islands, but I'd like to just lay out the best way to kill these things.  If you're around lvl 10 and you are a melee class like me you'll probably want to just camp the single spawn (island on the left coming from freeport).  The spawn is about 6 minutes tho, so you'll be full health and stuff before the next fight.  Then if you are a caster w/ pet or a little bit higher lvl melee, you can camp the double spawn on the island on the right and then swim across to the other island and kill the solo spawn.  This exp is REALLY great and you can get a bar of exp in like 20 minutes<BR>
<BR>
Ledor<BR>
Paladin of 16 Winters</font></td></tr></table>
